This has a black tea base.

515
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:44,500
Dianhong Black Tea.

516
00:31:44,500 --> 00:31:45,600
It has a strong taste.

517
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:47,200
Is it cream?

518
